title: Paul Simon - The Paul Simon Songbook (2004) [24-44 HD FLAC]
description:
The Paul Simon Songbook is the first solo studio album by Paul Simon. It was recorded in London and released in the UK in 1965 and was supposedly deleted in 1969 at Simon's request. It was made available in the U.S. as part of the LP box set Paul Simon: Collected Works (1981). (Wikipedia)
